        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "Went against them; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " being persuaded and encouraged so to do; partly to invent the mischiefs of a siege in Samaria, and the waste of all the rest of their country; and partly by the remembrance of their former success, and an expectation of the same assistance from God again. ",
        "children": []
