        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and the children of Israel pitched before them like two little flocks of kids: being few and weak, the two hundred and thirty two young men in one body, and the 7000 in another: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "but the Syrians filled the country: with their men, their horses, and their chariots. ",
        "children": [
